Sift @all-purpose flour{1%cup} into a #bowl{}; add @baking powder{1.5%tsp} and @salt{0.25%tsp} and whisk until fully incorporated.

Cut @butter{1%Tbsp} into flour mixture using a pastry cutter until evenly combined.
